snippet: MAIDMAN--Gail Ann Lowe. Fifth Avenue Synagogue records with profound sorrow the passing of its esteemed member and extends heartfelt sympathy to the bereaved. Eli Babich, Associate Rabbi Walter J. Molofsky, M.D., Chairman Jacob D. Gold, President 1/3
